Customers / Restaurants / Riders → FoodiHub Web & Mobile App (Flutter)
│
│──> REST API (Node.js + Express)
│
│──> Database (PostgreSQL / ReinHost Cloud)
│
│──> Real-time Order Tracking (Socket.IO / Firebase)
│
│──> Payment Gateway (Paystack / Flutterwave)
│
│──> Storage (AWS S3 / ReinHost Storage)
│
└──> Notifications (Firebase Cloud Messaging / SMTP)
